---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import Navbar from "../components/Navbar.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="Privacy Policy"
  description="How VividStack collects, uses, and protects information when you visit our site or get in touch."
>
  <Navbar />
  <main id="main-content" class="bg-vivid-cream text-vivid-navy min-h-screen pt-24 pb-20">
    <article class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6">
      <p class="text-vivid-mint font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.35em] text-xs mb-4">Legal</p>
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black uppercase tracking-tighter leading-tight mb-10" style="font-family: 'Space Grotesk', sans-serif;">
        Privacy Policy
      </h1>
      <div class="space-y-6 text-vivid-navy/85 leading-relaxed" style="font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;">
        <p class="text-sm text-vivid-navy/60">Last updated: April 3, 2026</p>
        <p>
          This policy describes how VividStack (“we”, “us”) handles information when you use vividstack.io. We keep
          this page short and plain; if you need specifics for a signed agreement, contact us and we will provide
          terms that match your project.
        </p>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-bold uppercase tracking-wide text-vivid-navy pt-4">What we collect</h2>
        <p>
          If you use our contact form, we receive the details you submit (such as name, email, and message) so we can
          reply. Our form provider may process submissions on our behalf under their own privacy terms.
        </p>
        <p>
          Like most sites, our hosting and analytics tools may log technical data (for example IP address, browser
          type, and approximate location) to keep the site secure and reliable.
        </p>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-bold uppercase tracking-wide text-vivid-navy pt-4">How we use it</h2>
        <p>
          We use contact submissions only to respond to you and to follow up on potential work. We do not sell your
          personal information.
        </p>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-bold uppercase tracking-wide text-vivid-navy pt-4">Your choices</h2>
        <p>
          You may ask what we hold about you, or request correction or deletion of contact details we received through
          the site, by emailing us from the address you used to write in.
        </p>
        <p class="pt-8">
          <a
            href="/"
            class="font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-xs text-vivid-navy border-b-2 border-vivid-mint hover:text-vivid-mint transition-colors focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-vivid-navy focus-visible:ring-offset-2 focus-visible:ring-offset-vivid-cream rounded-sm"
            >← Back to home</a>
        </p>
      </div>
    </article>
  </main>
</Layout>
